Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL STORY BY NATSU HYUUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THIS STORY IS A WORK OF FICTION, AND NAMES OF CHARACTERS,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ORGANIZATIONS, AND OTHER OFFICIAL TITLES ARE ALL FICTIONAL CREATIONS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.91,0:01:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope old man's doing well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Yesterday, after the garden party….
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The minister who ate the poison needed a lot of treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A patient should rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to them, I slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I shouldn't have slept until noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel weird not wearing my freckles…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've taken the day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not acceptable. If you need anything from me, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Your freckles…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel weird without them. Can I keep my face like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone rushed in demanding to know who my lady-in-waiting was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm so sorry about that. -It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gaoshun's been here since this morning. Do you want to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked bored, so I asked him to weed the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeding the garden…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was seated in a high position{\i} {\i1}at the garden party…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's such a diligent man…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure that man is also{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}collecting his own group{\i} {\i1}of lady-in-waiting fans.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,May we borrow the drawing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hongniang? -Yes, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like Hongniang's eyes{\i} {\i1}are glistening too…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you, from Sir Jinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the soup that Lady Gyokuyou was meant to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes. -How thoughtful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't eat it, all right? -I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver corrodes quickly. The soup is oxidized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-It won't taste good. -It's about the taste…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you carry this with your bare hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't touch the bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just dipped in a spoon to see if it was poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I wrapped it quickly with cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Snip, snip, snip. Clatter, clatter, clatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cotton, powder, and a brush? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At the apothecary I worked at, to prevent pranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we applied dye to containers you weren't supposed to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing a version of that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy. Add some powder to a rolled up cotton ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and apply it on the container.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll take off the extra powder using this brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here it is. -I see a white mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the spot where someone touched the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Any spot touched by a fingertip leaves some sort of mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is especially true for silverware that corrodes easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverware is always wiped down with a cloth before being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, the fingerprint left on this bowl now belongs to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who held this bowl after it was cleaned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The size and the location of the fingerprint
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to tell us how they held it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who held this bowl…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is there were a total of four people that held this bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Four people, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First are the three that touched{\i} {\i1}around the bowl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person who served the soup,{\i} {\i1}the person who carried the bowl,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the food taster for Lady Lishu,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and finally, one more. A third party{\i} {\i1}who touched the rim of the bowl…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's safe to assume that the poison was placed by this third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true, why is the fingerprint
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the food taster found on a high-ranking concubine's bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The food taster for Lady Lishu swapped it on purpose to trouble her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not knowing it was poison. -She swapped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A lady-in-waiting bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-To a high-ranking concubine? -So you don't believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to warn you in advance that this is my personal speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember Lady Lishu's outfit at the garden party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was a flashy, pink costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally, if a concubine{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chooses an outfit that is too similar{\i} {\i1}to Lady Gyokuyou's,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the attendants would recommend a different outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, the attendants would wear outfits that match their lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However, all her ladies-in-waiting were wearing white.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That made it seem as if{\i} {\i1}Lady Lishu, who was wearing pink,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was a clown who couldn't read the room.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attendants are meant to{\i} {\i1}support their lady.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even understand your own position as an attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you recommended a pink outfit for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Ah-Duo's attendants were reprimanding{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the incompetence{\i} {\i1}of Lady Lishu's attendants.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the rear palace,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by enemies, the only people concubines can trust
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are her own ladies-in-waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The young Lady Lishu merely followed the recommendation of her attendants
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and wore that outfit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and was shamed publicly on purpose.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She had no idea.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but they also swapped meals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to trouble Lady Lishu even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, without knowing it was poison. Though it ended up saving her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Their methods are dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Lishu is in the unique position{\i} {\i1}of being the former emperor's concubine,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then entering monkhood soon after.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She had been educated since childhood{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that a wife serves her husband.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People must think that it is{\i} {\i1}extremely immoral of her{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to marry her late husband's son.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the print left on the rim
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,belongs to the culprit who added the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-She held the rim to mix in the poison. -I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not dirty the area where a high-class person's lips touch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongniang taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are my speculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can I ask you one thing? -What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to cover for the food taster attendant yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just curious. I won't pursue this any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The life of an attendant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is worth much less than that of a concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the life of a food taster…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think of a good excuse for Sir Jinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to thank her in some way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for swapping the bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did get to taste the poison, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I really should've swallowed that soup…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's all. -I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clever at wording things, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that so? -It's clearly an inside job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, looking at the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You put it so simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this, I haven't slept since yesterday. I haven't even changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stop thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true nature is coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-No one's here. It's fine. -I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-That doesn't count. -Yes sir, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's no way to trick you, is there? -I've known you too long for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's troublesome to be taken care of by someone since you were born…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Jinshi. Your hair clip is still in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit. I totally forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hidden in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone figured out your true status.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep this, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat it so roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This can only be worn by those with special status. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-I know, I know. -No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for work…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-So, did you receive any hair clips? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave the rear palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-What did you say? -You can leave the rear palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the rear palace, you can't meet men from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but with special permission, men could take palace women outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what the hair clips being given out in the garden party mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alternately, you can use hair clips to ask to be let out of the rear palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks, Xiaolan. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao, thanks for the hawthorn fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've received four hair clips in total.{\i} {\i1}Out of those, two were from men.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. If they lost their "male parts," are they not called men…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apothecary!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Lihaku, a palace woman from the rear palace is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? An obligatory hair clip{\i} {\i1}was taken seriously…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'd hate to turn down{\i} {\i1}a beauty's invitation…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE JADE PAVILION: MAOMAO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I only gave a clip to one attendant from the Jade Pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how should I refuse her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-I hear that a lot. -Makeup really changes your looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And to call on me, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to visit home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Home? Do you even know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that it's possible to visit home temporarily
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can be my guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An attendant like you, asking a soldier like me to be a guarantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you called me all the way here just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I call you bold or reckless?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me to be used as a tool so you can visit home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I have something in mind to gift you for the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,THE VERDIGRIS HOUSE REFERRAL: MEIMEI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a flower-watching party at the Verdigris House?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Verdigris House?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking! That brothel is worth a year's salary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry. You'll understand once you see this referral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pairin. Joka. Meimei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this even more now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even high-ranking officials can barely afford those Three Princesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't believe me, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for taking your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait… -This is extremely unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask elsewhere. Please pretend I never asked…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this woman have other offers?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they're rose quartz{\i} {\i1}and silver hair clips?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're both of higher statuses than me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is this girl?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this mean that{\i} {\i1}this offer is legitimate…?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's too suspicious!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if it's really true,{\i} {\i1}I'd never have the chance to meet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Three Princesses again…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept my loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats, Maomao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that Maomao would beat us…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm so glad! -You must've met someone wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll bring back souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did you meet this man? -I just went with the flow…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, she doesn't know the meaning of hair clips at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. I feel the worst for him…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What face would he make?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh. Looks like there's going to be another drama…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jinshi, having finished his work,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}got bored and came to visit{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the day after Maomao's departure.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao left with some mysterious man…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To visit home for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My home, the pleasure district,{\i} {\i1}is not so far away.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After crossing the fence and moat{\i} {\i1}of the rear palace,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's within walking distance.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How extravagant, riding a carriage{\i} {\i1}for this distance…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the Three Princesses{\i} {\i1}at the Verdigris House{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are almost a god-like idol admired{\i} {\i1}even by regular people, after all…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an honor to be able to{\i} {\i1}witness them even once.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the pleasure district!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are girls that come to the district{\i} {\i1}wanting to become like their idols,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's not so easy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even for apprentices,{\i} {\i1}or courtesans-in-training,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's no guarantee she'd sell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-So this is the Verdigris House… -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,VERDIGRIS HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a historical brothel with a full lineup from middle-ranking to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest ranking courtesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How's everyone doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Long time no see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? What's wrong with this old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Grams, the owner of the Verdigris House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how I used to vomit poison back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So this is the very rich patron?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a handsome face, and a good body too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you got promoted young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, that's not something to say to someone's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, go get Pairin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-She should be taking tea today. -Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Pairin… -Are you confident in your arm muscles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I do train daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? Maybe this could work…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good luck out there! -Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao. I can't deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappearing for ten months without contacting us…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no other choice. You didn't read the wood tablet I sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did! Why else would I entertain a first-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is half of all I earned at the rear palace so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked them to pay in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Pairin we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't enough at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on. It's just tea! -Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really think nothing's happening with those arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-But that's out of my control… -Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll add it to your receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pay…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me all your best customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that one, someone young who I can keep squeezing out of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could a eunuch be a customer?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not him. The courtesans would fall{\i} {\i1}head over heels and run out of business.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd feel bad about offering Gaoshun{\i} {\i1}or the quack doctor…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao. Old man should be at home. Go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just crossing a street{\i} {\i1}from the pleasure district{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}changes the scenery completely.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dilapidated houses, beggars,{\i} {\i1}and the syphilitic streetwalkers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally arrived home.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out getting dye for my freckles that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But then…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have my term of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm going back in two days. -I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy, but I want a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go borrow the bath at the Verdigris House tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The rear palace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some trick of fate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW OF NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Next episode, "Wheat Stalks".{\i}
